{"tid":1516260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"基督徒既巴絲入一入嚟！","createTime":"2019-08-29T13:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T11:30:11.000Z","uid":302832,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e851dba85deadd17d17d295617f5abd90835eb35","tid":1516260,"uid":302832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:33:45.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n係依次運動入面<br />\n基督徒既參與度都幾高<br />\n但小妹我自己身處既教會都比較多藍絲廢老<br />\n真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身教會年輕人真係少<br />\n又多商人，個個經濟行先<br />\n好想知有冇巴絲同我一樣<br />\n好想知點樣處理情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de3556ea68f050abdb55506c50642a2404574e9","tid":1516260,"uid":314642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:00:01.000Z","msg":"好彩我間教會冇咁既情況，絲打唔開心唔好鬱住丫，搵人傾下～"},{"pid":"4bfe47d73f64eabfb47fa81e6ad47255bfb867a8","tid":1516260,"uid":302832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6de3556ea68f050abdb55506c50642a2404574e9","tid":1516260,"uid":314642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:00:01.000Z","msg":"好彩我間教會冇咁既情況，絲打唔開心唔好鬱住丫，搵人傾下～"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:03:30.000Z","msg":"多謝你吖，我都覺得教會應該少啲藍絲，但我個邊係深藍"},{"pid":"f193dc49a0504e3ff9c7d327cb18ce98c43fd999","tid":1516260,"uid":314642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bfe47d73f64eabfb47fa81e6ad47255bfb867a8","tid":1516260,"uid":302832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6de3556ea68f050abdb55506c50642a2404574e9","tid":1516260,"uid":314642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:00:01.000Z","msg":"好彩我間教會冇咁既情況，絲打唔開心唔好鬱住丫，搵人傾下～"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:03:30.000Z","msg":"多謝你吖，我都覺得教會應該少啲藍絲，但我個邊係深藍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:08:18.000Z","msg":"你唔介意的話我地可以傾下，我係絲"},{"pid":"7d24b1e8bfca3db8f307e07c010d8c38e10c1f52","tid":1516260,"uid":231818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img